# Workflow Governance Cycle

- Keep `docs/KICKOFF_AGENT_PROMPT.md` as orchestration entry and avoid process duplication across prompt files.
- Execute lesson delivery in stages using `.cursor/skills/lesson-stage-*`.
- Before release, run `node ./scripts/qa-workflow-audit.mjs` and keep `reports/workflow-audit/latest.json` as evidence.
- Any `BLOCKED` audit state is a release blocker.
- For each lesson, record a retro entry with `docs/lesson-retro-template.md`.
- Every 10-15 lessons, run cycle review with `docs/workflow-cycle-review-template.md`.
- Convert recurring errors into concrete updates to rules/skills/scripts.
